PhpTaskDaemon-WebStatus Introduction
------------------------------------
PhpTaskDaemon is a library for creating php daemons for unix environments.
The PhpTaskDaemon-WebStatus is a sub project of the PhpTaskDaemon project for 
monitoring PhpTaskDaemon activities. The sub project consists of a basic zend
framework application with a status and statistics controller. The status
controller is used for requesting the current activities of the daemon, while
the statistics controller can be used to view the amount of executed tasks over
time.


Features
--------
* View current activities of the PhpTaskDaemon
* View historical statistics of the PhpTaskDaemon


Requirements
------------
* PHP 5.3
* PhpTaskDaemon
* Zend Framework


Installation
------------
Basic installation 
* Extract the package
* Edit the configuration file: src/application/configs/daemon.ini
* Edit the file (doc/files/apache.conf) to your needs 
* Copy the edited apache conf to /etc/apache2/sites-available/phptaskdaemon
* Enable the phptaskdaemon site: a2enmod phptaskdaemon
* Restart the apache server


